Package io.ylab.walletservice.service

Class WalletInMemoryService

java.lang.Object
io.ylab.walletservice.service.WalletInMemoryService
public class WalletInMemoryService extends Object
Class which allow to create new players, find them, make debit/credit of player's account and see transactions history. All data store in memory
